{"tid":1814611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攬抄就黎成功，大家繼續努力","createTime":"2020-01-07T03:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T04:37:54.000Z","uid":271875,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3c3160ef69be89dabdd2b5cc969605c5507c95dc","tid":1814611,"uid":271875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:39:23.000Z","msg":"近排不停放風唔好捉鬼，好多人退出，我覺得有機會係風聲黎。<br />\n<br />\n啲小隊成立時無大示宣揚，退出時咁招搖，唔怕比人捉咩？我覺得有機會係放風比人感覺退緊潮。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦都比我地攬到換左人，我覺得攬抄開始成功令佢地驚，要加埋黃色經濟圈，繼續努力，我哋會有我地既自由。<br />\n<br />\n要佢地明白到一係放我地自由，一係我地一齊攬炒！"},{"pid":"ad488c13c4b37b96911fe4987d92d15d3a8f9b93","tid":1814611,"uid":2757,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"遊行時遊行<br />\n裝修時裝修<br />\n<br />\n遊行時唔好裝修<br />\n裝修時唔好阻膠<br />\n<br />\n適當時候就做適當嘅嘢，唔好撈埋嚟做瀨尿牛丸，各施其職<br />\n<br />\n講完"},{"pid":"554e3cadab7ece1d11149e1fea562d80dff27388","tid":1814611,"uid":8049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:32:10.000Z","msg":"我們都有一個夢想<br />\n<br />\n穩固黃色經濟圈成型 新系統迎接新模式<br />\n<br />\n抵制支付寶來襲，抗衡八達通賣港<br />\n<br />\n屬於我地新時代既支付系統。<br />\n[招兵買馬] <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1805119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1805119</a><br />\n[關注我們] <a href=\"https://t.me/TimesPayHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTimesPayHK&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=a5b07324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TimesPayHK</a>"},{"pid":"4b5a3b227b8f02f99f0547f83dc8d8942ff9ff80","tid":1814611,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eb2a0f9155c725a1a0ac9440368f4209760074","tid":1814611,"uid":72988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T04:34:40.000Z","msg":"明明呢幾日都講緊支那肺炎 今日訓醒就變曬都係捉鬼退場post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adb597e67d23b51ae09c56626e0692